Load dataset

Info from MouseGastrulationAtlas vignettes

T (Brachyury) knockout chimeras involving sixteen samples, from eight embryo pools at two timepoints. The injected cells in the T chimeras have knockouts for the T gene. They also contain the td-Tomato construct.

They contain an extra feature for expression of the td-Tomato. Cells derived from the injected cells (and thus are positive for td-Tomato) are marked in the colData field tomato. Information for the proper pairing of samples from the same embryo pools can be found in the colData field pool. Spliced count matrices are not provided.
